{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845622748,"sessionID":"ses_2875b0f1cffexK7aoZm6r9C9Vy","part":{"id":"prt_d78a5c045001IZvcgv0TzJ1BAc","messageID":"msg_d78a5b5ec001I0yoSoUpJUMKgC","sessionID":"ses_2875b0f1cffexK7aoZm6r9C9Vy","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-c6b5b3d544fc416fb042fbcf34826a16","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-006/design.md","limit":100,"offset":1},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-006/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-006 Design Document\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: AR-006 implements comprehensive sandbox deletion and lifecycle management for the AgentCube WorkloadManager. This enhancement provides reliable cleanup mechanisms for sandbox resources, handles both manual deletion requests and automatic cleanup of idle/expired sessions, and ensures proper resource management in Kubernetes environments.\n6: \n7: **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n8: **Language**: Go  \n9: **Size**: M  \n10: **Purpose**: Implement robust sandbox deletion, lifecycle management, and cleanup mechanisms with proper error handling and observability.\n11: \n12: ## Architecture\n13: \n14: ### Component Overview\n15: \n16: ```\n17: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n18: │                    WorkloadManager Sandbox Lifecycle              │\n19: │                                                                  │\n20: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n21: │  │                   HTTP API Layer                         │   │\n22: │  │  DELETE /v1/sessions/:sessionId → DeleteSession          │   │\n23: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n24: │                            │                                      │\n25: │                            ▼                                      │\n26: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n27: │  │              SandboxController (pkg/workloadmanager/      │   │\n28: │  │              controller/sandbox.go)                       │   │\n29: │  │  - DeleteSession()                                        │   │\n30: │  │  - GetSession()                                           │   │\n31: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n32: │                            │                                      │\n33: │              ┌─────────────┴─────────────┐                        │\n34: │              ▼                           ▼                        │\n35: │  ┌──────────────────────┐   ┌──────────────────────┐            │\n36: │  │  Kubernetes API      │   │   Redis Store        │            │\n37: │  │  (client-go)         │   │   (go-redis)         │            │\n38: │  │  - Delete Sandbox    │   │   - Delete Session   │            │\n39: │  │  - Delete Pod        │   │   - Get Sandbox      │            │\n40: │  └──────────────────────┘   └──────────────────────┘            │\n41: │                                                                   │\n42: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n43: │  │         GarbageCollector (pkg/workloadmanager/           │   │\n44: │  │         garbage_collector.go)                             │   │\n45: │  │  - Auto cleanup idle sandboxes                           │   │\n46: │  │  - Auto cleanup expired sandboxes                        │   │\n47: │  │  - Audit logging                                         │   │\n48: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n49: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n50: ```\n51: \n52: ### Deletion Flow\n53: \n54: **Manual Deletion Flow**:\n55: ```\n56: Client DELETE /v1/sessions/{sessionId}\n57:     ↓\n58: [Middleware] Auth & RBAC validation\n59:     ↓\n60: [Handler] HandleDeleteSandbox()\n61:     ↓\n62: [Store] GetSandbox(sessionId) → SandboxInfo\n63:     ↓\n64: [K8s] DeleteSandbox(namespace, sandboxId) → agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/Sandbox\n65:     ↓\n66: [Store] DeleteSandboxBySessionID(sessionId)\n67:     ↓\n68: Response: 200 OK {sessionId, deletedAt}\n69: ```\n70: \n71: **Automatic Cleanup Flow**:\n72: ```\n73: GarbageCollector.tick() (every 15s)\n74:     ↓\n75: [Store] ListInactiveSandboxes(idleThreshold) → expired sessions\n76:     ↓\n77: [Store] ListExpiredSandboxes(expiredThreshold) → idle sessions\n78:     ↓\n79: For each sandbox:\n80:     ↓\n81:     [K8s] DeleteSandbox(namespace, sandboxId)\n82:     ↓\n83:     [Store] DeleteSandboxBySessionID(sessionId)\n84:     ↓\n85:     [Audit] Record cleanup entry (reason, timestamp, success)\n86: ```\n87: \n88: ### Lifecycle States\n89: \n90: ```\n91: ┌──────────────┐\n92: │   Creating   │ ← CreateSandbox() → pending status\n93: └──────┬───────┘\n94:        │ Pod ready\n95:        ▼\n96: ┌──────────────┐\n97: │   Running    │ ← normal operation\n98: └──────┬───────┘\n99:        │ Activity timeout OR Max duration\n100:        ▼\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 848. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-006 Design Document\n\n## Overview\n\nAR-006 implements comprehensive sandbox deletion and lifecycle management for the AgentCube WorkloadManager. This enhancement provides reliable cleanup mechanisms for sandbox resources, handles both manual deletion requests and automatic cleanup of idle/expired sessions, and ensures proper resource management in Kubernetes environments.\n\n**Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n**Language**: Go  \n**Size**: M  \n**Purpose**: Implement robust sandbox deletion, lifecycle management, and cleanup mechanisms with proper error handling and observability.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Overview\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    WorkloadManager Sandbox Lifecycle              │\n│                                                                  │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-006/design.md","time":{"start":1775845622724,"end":1775845622746}}}}
