{"type":"text","timestamp":1775845636362,"sessionID":"ses_2875b0f1cffexK7aoZm6r9C9Vy","part":{"id":"prt_d78a5e0fb001SKnDmqz1vD7sF3","messageID":"msg_d78a5c40e001sTOr5fIXGtJHtn","sessionID":"ses_2875b0f1cffexK7aoZm6r9C9Vy","type":"text","text":"## AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理\n\n### What Was Completed\n\n**Core Implementation (Tasks 1-14):**\n- ✅ Package structure and constants (defaults.go)\n- ✅ Store interface extensions for lifecycle management (store.go)  \n- ✅ Kubernetes client wrapper for deletion operations (k8s_client.go)\n- ✅ SandboxController deletion methods (controller/sandbox.go)\n- ✅ API types for deletion operations (api/types.go)\n- ✅ HTTP Handler for manual deletion (handler/sandbox.go)\n- ✅ DELETE route registration in HTTP router (server/server.go)\n- ✅ GarbageCollector structure and lifecycle (garbage_collector.go)\n- ✅ GarbageCollector tick() method for idle/expired cleanup\n- ✅ GarbageCollector deleteSandbox() method with audit logging\n- ✅ GarbageCollector recordAudit() method\n- ✅ GarbageCollector integration into server startup/shutdown\n- ✅ Session expiration and idle timeout tracking\n- ✅ Unit tests for core components (8 test files)\n\n**Key Features Implemented:**\n- Manual deletion via DELETE /v1/sessions/:sessionId\n- Automatic cleanup of idle sandboxes (15 min timeout)\n- Automatic cleanup of expired sandboxes (8 hour TTL)\n- Idempotent deletion operations (handles NotFound gracefully)\n- Audit logging for all cleanup operations\n- Store and Kubernetes resource synchronization\n\n### What Was Deferred\n\n**Tasks 15-20:**\n- ❌ Integration tests (Task 14-15) - No end-to-end integration test suite\n- ❌ Metrics and observability (Task 16) - No Prometheus metrics implementation\n- ❌ Error handling enhancements (Task 17) - Basic error handling exists, no retry logic\n- ❌ RBAC permissions and security (Task 18) - No RBAC manifest updates\n- ❌ Documentation (Task 19) - No README or API documentation created\n- ❌ CHANGELOG entry and final verification (Task 20) - CHANGELOG not updated\n- ❌ Implementation summary document - IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md remains empty\n\n**Summary:**\nThe core sandbox deletion and lifecycle management functionality is fully implemented and tested (14/20 tasks completed, 70% complete). All critical features for manual deletion, automatic garbage collection, and basic error handling are working. Deferred items focus on operational aspects: comprehensive testing, observability, security hardening, and documentation.","time":{"start":1775845636360,"end":1775845636360}}}
